PrecisRe-appointment of YVES BOISROND, of Ville Mont-Royal, Quebec, and GIUSEPPE MANNO, of Laval, Quebec, as full-time members of the Convention Refugee Determination Division of the Immigration and Refugee Board (Montreal Regional Office), to hold office during good behaviour for a term of three years, effective June 14, 2001.
